{"ticker": "SHIELD_AI", "company": "Shield AI", "weight_sum": 4.92, "etfs": ["ARKUX", "ARKSX", "ARKVX"], "is_private": true, "query": "\"Shield AI\" -is:retweet min_faves:10 since_time:1777550940 until_time:1777637340", "n_fetched": 1, "n_kept": 1, "n_dropped": 0, "kept": [{"type": "tweet", "id": "2049941502160474403", "url": "https://x.com/dperi84/status/2049941502160474403", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/dperi84/status/2049941502160474403", "text": "Shield AI announces opening of an office in New Delhi to support its growing partnership with the Indian Ministry of Defence and advance its work with the broader industry ecosystem.\n\nShield AI has established a wholly owned subsidiary, Shield AI India, to support software integration, engineering, and autonomy development, and to grow indigenous engineering and software development capabilities for India.\n\nIn January, the company\u00a0announced that its V-BAT vertical take-off and landing (VTOL) reconnaissance UAS was selected by the Indian Army. Under the program, the Indian Army will receive V-BATs and licenses for Shield AI\u2019s Hivemind autonomy software, which will be integrated into the V-BAT platform.\n\nIn December 2025, Shield AI in partnership JSW Defence commenced construction of its facility for next-gen UAS at Hyderabad to manufacture V-BAT domestically with an investment of $90 million. Facility to also function as a global production hub.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 8, "replyCount": 0, "likeCount": 23, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 1157, "createdAt": "Thu Apr 30 19:58:34 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 3, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2049941502160474403", "displayTextRange": [0, 273], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "dperi84", "url": "https://x.com/dperi84", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/dperi84", "id": "208165466", "name": "Dinakar Peri", "isVerified": false, "isBlue